      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HURRICANE (2) is a well performed dog who recorded his 7th career win last time out at The Meadows (29.92). Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Can make it two on the bounce. EVENTUATE (8) is an accomplished stayer with a great record at the longer races. Kept coming to fill the minor placings over 600m at The Meadows (34.77) in a Grade 5. Goes very well at the trip finding the frame in each of four starts. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Leading chance. AVENGEMENT (4) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.34. Has a tricky draw to overcome but has a good record over this journey. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Should feature again. NIGEL DEVERE (1) warrants respect following a recent placing in a tight finish.",
